                     <interp inst="t17770910-70-off339" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a striped cotton waistcoat, value 1 s. six linen shirts, value 12 s. six linen stocks, value 6 s. a pair of silk stockings, value 2 s. a pair of thread stockings, value 1 s. a linen handkerchief, value 6 d. and a canvass bag, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770910-70-victim556" type="victimName">
                     Edward
                      Cooper
                  <interp inst="t17770910-70-victim556" type="surname" value="Cooper"></interp>
